Serialized Fields

forcedValue

String forcedValue
The String representation to be returned by toString if a form other than a formatted Date is desired. Setting this value to anything other than null (the initialized value) will override the date formatting and instead return this String.

syntaxString

String syntaxString
If this TimeSpec was created by parsing a syntax String, this is the unparsed value. This is provided purely as a convenience and is not required to be set or used.

format

The DateFormat object to be used to format dates.
